<p><strong>Week 1-2 of building:</strong> High time investment, significant frustration with webhook and Zapier configurations. Normal. Push through.</p>

<p><strong>Week 3 onward:</strong> System runs without involvement. New applications arrive, move through the pipeline, and emerge as active partners without you sending a single email.</p>

<p><strong>At scale:</strong> With 10+ new applications per week, the ROI of building this system becomes obvious. A manual process at that volume would require dedicated staff. The automated system handles it on $400/mo in software.</p>

